OOC: Kinger just let him go he's a disembodied spark, he can't bother you.

::Enertron's Spark::
        He "saw," for lack of a better word, the Matrix of war emerging and 
flew out the door.  He slowed the beam by using his own energy against it.  
His energy was dismally weak and slowed the beam only a tiny amount but it 
was enough to get him out of the ship and into the air where no bot, no 
matter how godlike, would be able to catch him.
